      <title>河野太郎宣布参选，日本领导人竞选升温</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/who-could-replace-kishida-candidates-who-could-be-japan-s-new-prime-minister</link>
      <description><![CDATA[现任日本数字化转型大臣的一位政治异见人士成为第三位参加下一任首相竞选的议员，他呼吁财政紧缩，并强调自己在内阁担任各种职务的经验。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/who-could-replace-kishida-candidates-who-could-be-japan-s-new-prime-minister</guid>
